---
title: Cheesy Melt in the Middle Bacon Burger with Wedges and Balsamic Pea Shoot Salad
description: Inspired by the classic American cheeseburger, this Cheesy Melt in the Middle Beef Burger is sure to suit everyone's tastes. Instead of piling the cheese on top, fold your beef patties around it for a simple way to try something new!
